                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/storm/blob/master/storm-client/src/jvm/org/apache/storm/cluster/StormClusterStateImpl.java#L650-L660&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;StormClusterStateImpl reportError function&lt;/a&gt; is called, it will get all the children of &lt;/p&gt;
